invalid type: string "Title: Data Exfiltration\nSeverity: CRITICAL\nTags: exfiltration, data-loss, dns-tunneling, large-upload\nMITRE ATT&CK: T1041 - Exfiltration Over C2 Channel\nExplanation: Data exfiltration is the unauthorized transfer of data from the organization's network. Attackers often use encrypted channels, DNS tunneling, or legitimate cloud services to evade detection.\n~ĸĸĸĸĸĸĸĸĸĸĸĸ